{"tid":1657228,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"不要離他們而去 - 李碧華","createTime":"2019-10-16T03:51:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-16T04:04:16.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4d656c3b8080f6cfb1b427942c27b32268bf8718","tid":1657228,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T03:51:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20191016/20787463/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191016%2F20787463%2F&d=TC1Ad7l9MtPLjBCdpR1LVg0QAWntaMGUWBfwPSaCbl8%3D&h=ef632169\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191016%2F20787463%2F&h=9f5b5c55\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20191016/20787463/</a><br />\n<br />\n不要離他們而去 - 李碧華<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20191016/large/1571130120_0a07.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20191016%2Flarge%2F1571130120_0a07.jpg&h=f6b2ecf9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n現今教育局淪為政治鷹犬，荒謬到施壓令大中小學幼稚園幼兒園學生，校內外不得戴口罩，過氣政棍還倡革除「暴徒」學籍，把十幾歲少年踢出校？孤立無援，自生自滅？絕非「有教無類」之教育情操，學生、教師、校長、家長面對「殺氣」摧毀，難道屈從？<br />\n<br />\n事有因果，人有良知，只是好些人賣了、掉了、親手扼殺了，以換取權勢名利和主子賞賜。猶幸有中學校董會表示，不會革除示威中受槍傷學生之學籍，「我們絕不會離他而去」。<br />\n<br />\n日前有警員疑被一名19歲中六學生刺傷頸部，靜脈受傷無生命危險，警方表示未能在現場找到相關兇器，涉嫌的學生被捕扣留，初控「意圖謀殺」後改為「有意圖而傷人」罪，最高刑罰是終身監禁。而15歲彥霖赤裸浮屍，更似被謀殺疑點重重，警方卻說無可疑急急火化。<br />\n<br />\n所有案件要待法庭判決，所有人（包括不相識的市民）關注，只因黑警濫捕濫暴，連記者醫護亦遭酷刑毒打，明目張膽，年輕示威者會否繼續被自殺或變成浮屍？世上沒有無緣無故的愛恨，卻有無緣無故的「消失」。大人們請不要離他們而去，也不要如理大陳姓撐警講師般，在鏡頭下未與任何人有身體接觸自行仰倒地上，卻誣學生推跌3次，枉為人師──有片有真相，暗室暴虐拒交CCTV則掩埋血腥。 <br />\n<br />\n李碧華<br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com"},{"pid":"ac10d89c91dc81e43e3a61cc9558779296f5566d","tid":1657228,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T03:52:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PgjbDGh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPgjbDGh.jpg&h=e5447ac9&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"841de09afcb53a4f13e8dac3e2eaba4ac9ee1ff3","tid":1657228,"uid":250558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T04:04:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JyRmoa3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJyRmoa3.jpg&h=d0e76ef6&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}